  <p>
   <div xlink:href="c9sc01313j-ga.jpg" id="ga" position="float" orientation="portrait" class="graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>We investigate how digital quantum computers may be used to calculate molecular vibrational properties, such as energy levels and spectral information.
  </p>
